","text":"It is always outrageously furious. If it gives chase, it will tenaciously track the target no matter how far."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it catches up."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"If approached while asleep, it may awaken and angrily give chase in a groggy state of semi-sleep."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It becomes wildly furious if it even senses someone looking at it. It chases anyone that meets its glare."},{"version":"black","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"white","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder."},{"version":"x","text":"It stops being angry only when nobody else is around. To view this moment is very difficult."},{"version":"y","text":"It is always outrageously furious. If it gives chase, it will tenaciously track the target no matter how far."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time."},{"version":"sun","text":"It has been known to become so angry that it dies as a result. Its face looks peaceful in death, however."},{"version":"moon","text":"Some researchers theorize that Primeape remains angry even when inside a Pok\u00e9 Ball."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It will never forgive opponents who have angered it. Even after it has beaten them down until they can\u2019t move, it never ever forgives."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"The blood vessels in its brain are sturdier than those of other Pok\u00e9mon, so it can stay healthy despite its constant raging."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"It stops being angry only when nobody else is around. To view this moment is very difficult."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"It stops being angry only when nobody else is around. To view this moment is very difficult."}],"evo":{"name":"mankey","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"primeape","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"annihilape","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-move","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/57.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.c